snippet.title: The Crush House - Official Release Date Trailer | Devolver Digital 2024
snippet.description: Get a fresh look at The Crush House in this latest trailer for the upcoming simulation game. The trailer gives you a look at the drama and romance of this reality TV show game. The Crush House will be available on PC on August 9, 2024, and a demo is available now. Film and produce 1999's hottest reality TV show: The Crush House! Select a crush-worthy cast, satisfy voracious audiences and keep the show on air to uncover the sinister secrets behind this darkly comic thirst-person shooter.
